  "notes": "Complex revival monster. Starts with the Adaptable power, which allows it to revive twice. After each death, its form changes and it gains new powers. Multi-Claw's hit count starts at 3 and increases by 1 with each use. The Adaptable power grants revives with PainfulStabs after the first death and Nemesis after the second. Once Adaptable expires, the monster stays dead. Each respawn increases the monster's size by 10% (Respawns * 0.1)."
